Terri N wrote a review Feb 2024
2 contributions
I was asked to leave a review at checkout
The service is good. Room is clean. They do ask for you to leave a review at check-out and seem persistent. Other than that, everything is fine. The hotel is in good location. The hospital is nearby. Many local food and bars nearby. Da Nang is a safe city to travel.
Date of stay: February 2024
