Great stay
My stay was great and staff were extremely friendly. Overall, the hotel was clean and well maintained. The included free breakfast was nice and offer different dishes daily. The hotel was in walking distance to all the good food and attractions. Highly recommended.
Excursion632345 wrote a review Feb 2024
Comfortable yet modern
From first step in to last step out, the service and hospitality was superb. The bell hop service guy downstairs was super helpful as well as the receptionist on the 6th floor. The breakfast buffet was exceptionally delicious with all types of food. We booked a two bedroom corner suite and the views were to die for. Comfortable yet modern. Definitely going to come back and stay at this hotel.
