Frequently Asked Questions about G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang
Which popular attractions are close to G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Nearby attractions include Con Market (0.3 miles), Tahoe Tailors (0.2 miles), and Da Nang Fine Arts Museum (0.05 miles).
See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include free wifi, free breakfast, and a pool.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Top room amenities include a minibar, air conditioning, and a flat screen TV.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Guests can enjoy free breakfast, an on-site restaurant, and a lounge during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Yes, free parking, a parking garage, and paid private parking nearby are available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Conveniently located restaurants include Le Bambino, Mi Quang 1A, and SUSHI-Be.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
Yes, guests have access to a pool, a sauna, and a yoga room during their stay.
Does G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang have airport transportation?
Yes, G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Does G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang offer any business services?
Yes, it conveniently offers a business center, meeting rooms, and a banquet room.
Which languages are spoken by the staff at G8 Luxury Hotel and Spa Da Nang?
The staff speaks multiple languages, including English, Russian, Chinese, Japanese, Vietnamese, and Korean.
